 LOADED WITH A GIRL UP TO BAT. OUR PITCHER THROUGH A SERIES OF PITCHES THROWS 3 BALLS TO HER BUT THE UMPIRE DOES NOT WALK HER. THE NEXT PITCH IS POPPED UP FOR THE LAST OUT OF THE INNING. AFTER WE GET OFF THE FIELD THE UMPIRES CONVERSE (WHICH SHOULD HAVE HAPPENED BEFORE THE PITCH) AND DECIDE THE PITCH COUNT WAS ERRANT. BECAUSE OF OUR TEAMS OBJECTION (I.E. ONCE THE GIRL HIT THE BALL IT WAS PUT INTO PLAY THUS NULLIFYING ANY PROTEST {MUCH LIKE AN APPEAL PLAY FOR A PLAYER TAGGING}). THE UMPIRES WENT TO THE UIC. AND HE SAID THAT THE INNING SHOULD NOT HAVE ENDED (BASICALLY THAT THE UMPIRE IN THE FIELD MESSED UP AND SHOULD HAVE CALLED TIME). OH AND JUST FOR THE RECORD THE NEXT GUY UP HITS A GRAND SLAM. WAS THIS AN UMPIRE MESS UP AS WE THINK OR WAS THE RIGHT CALL MADE??????? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/boklahomasoftball.showUserPublicProfile?gid=batpimp>BatPimp</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>ezOP</span><br>  Posts: 423<br> <font color=#8B0000>(6/13/03 6:50 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_exclamation_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: ANOTHER BOOMER SCREWING???!!!!!!</span><hr size=1> Sounds to me like you walked her, they blew the call, then did whatever it took to make the situation right.  I don't see how you can throw her three balls and be upset because she ended up getting a walk. Obviously the umps were green and didn't realize the situation. You are asking for an umps mistake to help you win a game?<br>
<br>
By the book, the inning should have ended. You're right, too late for an appeal.<br>
By all that is right in the world, the girl should have walked.<br>
<br>
Two ways to solve it from your side....don't throw three balls to the girl or don't give up the grand slam. <br>
<br>
From the other team's view they did absolutely everything right and deserved to win.<br>
<br>
